The cattleprod is a quest item obtained during the Sheep Herder quest. It spawns next to the incinerator in the fenced off area north of Ardougne. It is used to prod Sick-looking sheep in order to move them from their habitats into the pen to be incinerated. It has the same combat stats as a Bronze dagger.
